WEBVTT

00:08:26.520 --> 00:08:30.162
and as customers who consume them.

00:08:30.162 --> 00:08:34.280
But this maximizing participation thing

00:08:34.280 --> 00:08:35.899
doesn't happen by accident.

00:08:35.899 --> 00:08:37.868
It doesn't happen by itself.

00:08:37.868 --> 00:08:41.597
It requires effort and investment,

00:08:41.597 --> 00:08:44.027
which is why all

00:08:44.027 --> 00:08:47.258
highly prosperous capitalist democracies

00:08:47.258 --> 00:08:49.807
are characterized by massive investments

00:08:49.807 --> 00:08:52.372
in the middle class and the infrastructure

00:08:52.372 --> 00:08:55.240
that they depend on.

00:08:55.240 --> 00:08:57.239
We plutocrats need to get this

00:08:57.239 --> 00:09:00.378
trickle-down economics thing behind us,